🌸Gifted /Promo🌸 Sugar overload! Someone is missing me so much and surprised me with not one but three boxes of @krispykremesingapore doughnuts!
.
@krispykremesingapore said there’s six reasons to smile but I got eighteen instead. .
Promotion: Get a FREE Half Dozen Orginal Glazed doughnuts with ANY Dozen doughnut purchased online across all delivery platforms @foodpandasg , @grabfoodsg and @deliveroo_sg .
.
FREE Delivery is applicable via @foodpandasg only. Drop a note in the special request for a customised message on our doughnut boxes! Promotion is valid until the end of May. While stocks last, T&Cs apply. .
Thank you for the sweetness and love and for sending these over (don’t want me to mention you but I can still thank you here).
